headline: Lam Research Donates Leading-Edge Etch System to Accelerate Nanofabrication R&D at UC Berkeley
summary: Lam Research Corp. (Nasdaq: LRCX) today announced the donation of its innovative multi-chamber semiconductor etching system to the Marvell Nanofabrication Laboratory at the University of California, Berkeley to advance research and development (R&D) for next-generation chip technologies.
